{
  "page": "Frozen Ford",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Frozen Ford</b> was the site in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> where, according to song, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> met the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> in battle when they went south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Bael_the_Bard\" title=\"Bael the Bard\">Bael the Bard</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/King-beyond-the-Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King-beyond-the-Wall\">King-beyond-the-Wall</a>, met his son, the young Lord Stark, at the Frozen Ford and died there rather than kill his son.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Ford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Jon VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"n